<BaseLayout title="Method — Signal Underway">
  <div class="article" style="margin-top:14px">
    <h2 style="margin:0 0 10px 0">Method</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p><strong>1) Start with a trace.</strong> A tender, patent, budget line, satellite change, regulatory note, or corporate filing.</p>
      <p><strong>2) Corroborate.</strong> We look for repetition across sources and geographies.</p>
      <p><strong>3) Frame implications.</strong> We present multiple plausible futures — and we explicitly avoid certainty.</p>
      <p><strong>4) Invite correction.</strong> If you have primary sources, send them to <strong>tips@yourdomain</strong>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
